  "texts": [
    "This allow for BERT to try and predict the next sentence.",
    "The MLM parameter is set as a percentage of the sentence that will be masked.",
    "The norm is to set this parameter between 5% and 20% of words that are masked within the sentence.",
    "To address some of the shortfalls of BERT, the Robustly optimized BERT approach (RoBERTa) [16] was created and has exceeded the performance of all of the post-BERT methods.",
    "The following modifications were made to create the superior engine: First, the model was trained longer; second, the next sentence prediction objective was removed; third, the model was trained on longer sequences."
  ],
